        {
            "id": 6384294,
            "title": "外資再賣580億元 3月以來賣超達5549億元大砍台積電逾15萬張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股今 (13) 日下跌 181.54 點收 33400.32 點，外資再賣 580 億元、連二賣，大砍面板股，賣超群創 27 萬張最多，並調節晶圓代工、記憶體等族群。累計外資單周賣超達 2379 億元；3 月以來 10 個交易日賣超 5549 億元，其中台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 遭賣超 15.43 萬張。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6384294/l/df928d0842c269bcaa4bbe523ac477fe.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">外資再賣580億元 3月以來賣超達5549億元大砍台積電逾15萬張。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>外資賣超最大量為群創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3481:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3481\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3481-TW</a>)27.46 萬張，其次為友達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2409:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2409\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2409-TW</a>)5.91 萬張，另有彩晶 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6116:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6116\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6116-TW</a>)1.57 萬張，台積電 1.27 萬張、聯電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2303-TW</a>)2.53 萬張、華邦電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2344:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2344\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2344-TW</a>)1.74 萬張、南亞科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2408:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2408\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2408-TW</a>)1.21 萬張。</p></section><section>\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>傳產方面，外資賣超塑化相關的中石化 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1314:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1314\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1314-TW</a>)2.92 萬張、遠東新 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1402:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1402\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1402-TW</a>)1.79 萬張、台塑化 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6505:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6505\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6505-TW</a>)1.17 萬張，以及中鋼 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2002:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2002\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2002-TW</a>)2.53 萬張，航運的陽明 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2609:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2609\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2609-TW</a>)1.25 萬張、華航 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2610:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2610\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2610-TW</a>)2.19 萬張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>金融股賣超臺企銀 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2834:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2834\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2834-TW</a>)1.90 萬張及台新新光金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2887:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2887\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2887-TW</a>)1.44 萬張、富邦金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2881:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2881\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2881-TW</a>)1.19 萬張等較多，ETF 則賣超元大台灣 50(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:0050:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/0050\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">0050-TW</a>)5.86 萬張、主動統一台股增長 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00981A:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00981A\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00981A-TW</a>)1.35 萬張、國泰台灣領袖 50(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00922:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00922\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00922-TW</a>)1.09 萬張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>外資買超旺宏 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2337:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2337\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2337-TW</a>)3.44 萬張最多，另有 PCB 族群定穎投控 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3715:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3715\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3715-TW</a>)1.32 萬張、景碩 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3189:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3189\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3189-TW</a>)5,495 張、欣興 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3037:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3037\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3037-TW</a>)4,855 張、臻鼎 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4958:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4958\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4958-TW</a>)3,984 張、聯茂 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6213:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6213\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6213-TW</a>)3,860 張、華通 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2313:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2313\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2313-TW</a>)3,839 張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>其餘獲買超的電子股分別為鼎元 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2426:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2426\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2426-TW</a>)5,794 張、昇陽半導體 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8028:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8028\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8028-TW</a>)4,194 張、緯創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3231:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3231\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3231-TW</a>)3,895 張、台虹 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8039:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8039\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8039-TW</a>)3,856 張、愛普 *(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6531:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6531\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6531-TW</a>)2,988 張等；傳產有南亞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1303-TW</a>)2.74 萬張、新纖 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1409:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1409\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1409-TW</a>)9,053 張、華新 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1605:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1605\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1605-TW</a>)7,184 張等。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>金融股方面，外資買超第一金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2892:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2892\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2892-TW</a>)6,434 張、玉山金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2884:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2884\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2884-TW</a>)4,771 張等較多，ETF 則以元大滬深 300 正 2(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00637L:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00637L\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00637L-TW</a>)1.05 萬張、國泰永續高股息 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00878:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00878\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00878-TW</a>)6,421 張、期元大 S&amp;P 石油 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00642U:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00642U\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00642U-TW</a>)4,488 張等較多。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
